Brand pillars:
	Reliable
	Empowering
	___

If someone is 5 - 10 meters within range, greet them

Structure all your communication around two goals:
	-> protecting your brand
	-> building relationships

-> you want to be in control of what other pwople are hearing, reading, and seeing about you before they meet you

-> Your relationship history
	- How you've solved problems and achieved goals
	- The experiences that influenced you along the way

	* Tell yourself the story of your career
	* express your values in a tangible way

A brand is an emotion, a connection, a perception, a moment and a memory

