Networking

Create a network map
	* names
	* depth
	* note or 2 on expertise

	-> Learn about their projects and professional interests

--

Managing up

1. What can I take off from your plate that you don't like doing
2. Which meeting can I go to for you and report back
3. What project teams should I get involved with to bring more exposure to our department

--

Create a shared bundle

-> Keep it simple
	* How they got to their current position
	* What do they like best about their work

-> Find commonalities
-> Ask deepeer questions
	* Is there something in your past that makes what you do now special
	* wow, thats interesting, what was your key takeaway

Every Relationship is an Assignment